{"id":638308,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/03/水母真探社｜难以置信！李文亮的微博下方，诞生/","date":"2020-03-13T05:54:20Z","modified":"2020-03-13T05:54:20Z","title":"水母真探社｜难以置信！李文亮的微博下方，诞生了互联网的奇迹","content":"<p>李文亮医生在2020年2月7日离世，至今已经整整35天。</p>\n<p>然而最近，有很多网友发现，李文亮在2020年2月1日发出的最后一条微博，居然一直活着。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮-2.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638312\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"553\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮-2.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮-2-271x300.jpeg 271w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮-2-768x849.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>在这条微博的下方，每天都有成千上万的网友给他写留言，几乎是以每分钟增加一条留言的速度持续增长，从未停歇。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮3.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638314\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"124\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮3.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮3-300x74.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮3-768x190.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有网友给李医生留言，希望他能给自己在天堂的父亲问好。</p>\n<p>有网友捡到了一只流浪猫，也来李医生这里碎碎念：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮4-1.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638316\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮4-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"243\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮4-1.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮4-1-300x146.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮4-1-768x373.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>面临考试的孩子们，压力山大：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮5-1.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638317\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮5-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"143\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮5-1.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮5-1-300x86.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮5-1-768x220.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮6.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638318\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"191\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮6.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮6-300x115.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮6-768x294.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮7.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638319\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"169\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮7.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮7-300x101.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮7-768x260.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>怀了孕的女网友，半夜因为恶心而惊醒：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮8.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638320\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮8.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮8-300x215.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮8-768x551.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有恋爱烦恼的网友数量惊人：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮9.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638321\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"167\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮9.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮9-300x100.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮9-768x256.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮10.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638322\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮10.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"141\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮10.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮10-300x84.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮10-768x216.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>甚至连好事将近，准备要见对方家长了，也会产生烦躁和忧虑：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮11.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638323\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮11.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"123\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮11.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮11-300x74.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮11-768x189.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>除了这些自我倾诉型的网友外，还有很多网友是来报喜的：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮12.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638324\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮12.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"197\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮12.jpeg 824w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮12-300x118.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮12-768x302.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮13.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638325\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮13.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"110\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮13.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮13-300x66.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮13-768x169.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>当然了，也有报忧的：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮14.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638327\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮14.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"197\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮14.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮14-300x118.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮14-768x302.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>甚至有股民跑到李医生这里聊起了行情：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮15.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638328\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮15.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮15.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮15-300x123.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮15-768x314.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>还有人流露出了藏不住的喜悦：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮16.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638329\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮16.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮16.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮16-300x119.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮16-768x304.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>很多网友看过李文亮的历史微博，知道李文亮是个吃货，于是经常跑到这里来分享美食图片：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮17.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638330\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮17.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮17.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮17-300x255.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮17-768x652.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮18.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638331\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮18.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"263\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮18.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮18-300x158.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮18-768x403.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮19.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638332\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮19.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"327\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮19.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮19-300x196.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮19-768x502.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>李文亮喜欢吃车厘子的事情广为流传，很多网友触景生情：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮20-1.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638333\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮20-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮20-1.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮20-1-300x187.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮20-1-768x480.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮20-1-400x250.jpeg 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮21-1.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638334\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮21-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"184\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮21-1.jpeg 796w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮21-1-300x110.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮21-1-768x283.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>半夜失眠党非常多：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮22-1.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638335\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮22-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮22-1.jpeg 776w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮22-1-300x148.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮22-1-768x380.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>还有人竟然大早上醒来后，发现自己梦见了李医生：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮24-1.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638336\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮24-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮24-1.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮24-1-300x171.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮24-1-768x437.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮25-1.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638337\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮25-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"304\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮25-1.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮25-1-300x182.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮25-1-768x467.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>由于最近两天天气很好，感受到春暖花开的朋友非常多：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮26-2.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638338\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮26-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"307\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮26-2.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮26-2-300x184.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮26-2-768x471.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮27.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638339\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮27.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"193\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮27.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮27-300x116.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮27-768x296.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮28.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-638340\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮28.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"207\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮28.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮28-300x124.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/03/李文亮28-768x318.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>水母浏览了整整3个小时，不知不觉间，已泪流满面。</p>\n<p>是的老李，春天来了。</p>\n<p>不知道如果你有在天之灵，是否真的会看到网友们的这些留言。</p>\n<p>无论这些留言是报喜还是报忧、满满正能量又或者是淡淡的忧伤，都能让我们感受到同样的特点：人性。</p>\n<p>而人性的背后，是满满的温暖和感动。</p>\n<p>老李，想必你在同学群里发出预警信息的时候，完全不会想到今天的这一幕吧。</p>\n<p>你要是还活着，多好。</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[38895,38912,39707],"tags":[19986,39920,39775,39753,39648,12371]}